  "description": "External works include the installation of window box grills to the first floor front elevation;  replacement of grey quarry tiles on front door threshold with encaustic black and white tiles; the erection of two sets of steps in Portland stone and replacement of existing sandstone paving with Portland stone; replacement of existing softwood timber trellis and fencing with hardwood; reparation of garden walls; replacement of rear garden timber door and timber door to terrace with powder coated aluminium bi-fold doors; replacement of lower ground floor timber sash window with powder coated aluminium unit; replacement of timber velux window on rear elevation with a conservation rooflight; and clearance of existing garden and replacement of 1no. tree with new planting. Internal works include the reinstatement of 3no. fireplaces on lower ground, ground and first floor. Creation of window opening in previously blocked door opening. Infill of ground floor door opening, and the reinstatement of period cornice in first floor bedroom. Full Planning application (ref. P2017/0257/FUL) also submitted.",
